Package: Linnorm
Type: Package
Title: Linear model and normality based normalization method (Linnorm)
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2016-03-09
Author: Ken Shun Hang Yip <shunyip@bu.edu> <u3003188@connect.hku.hk>,
	Pak Chung Sham <pcsham@hku.hk>, Junwen Wang <junwen@uw.edu>
Maintainer: Ken Shun Hang Yip <shunyip@bu.edu>
Description: A Normalization method for RNA-seq Expression data or large scale
    count data for parametric tests. This package also includes several functions for the simulation of RNA-seq count data based on known distributions.
